comments: Young (ATL) gathers the ball on his right foot then legally steps with his left foot and immediately calls for a timeout.
Simmons (PHI) reaches behind Young (ATL) and makes contact with the ball to dislodge the ball, then makes marginal follow-through contact with Young's front.
Huerter (ATL) commits a take foul on Simmons (PHI).
Simmons (PHI) reached behind Young (ATL) as he dribbles and makes contact with the ball to dislodge the ball.
Simmons (PHI) makes incidental foot to foot contact with Young (ATL) during the inbound play.
After the hand-off, Collins (ATL) turns into Curry's (PHI) path and makes contact with Curry that affects his ability to defend on-ball.
Curry's (PHI) and Huerter's (ATL) arms briefly become interlocked as they move off-ball.
Embiid (PHI) and Capela (ATL) briefly engage and disengage during the driving shot attempt by Harris (PHI).
Curry (PHI) makes contact with Huerter (ATL) that affects his ability to get to the pass.
Capela (ATL) legally firms up in Thybulle's (PHI) path and does not deliver any contact during the pick.
Thybulle (PHI) makes contact with Huerter's (ATL) head during his jump shot attempt.
Hill (PHI) briefly grasps Capela's (ATL) arm as they engage during the screen.
Gallinari (ATL) makes contact with the ball and dislodges the ball from Embiid (PHI).
Collins' (ATL) momentum continues to bring him forward and Collins makes contact with Milton's (PHI) body that affects his trajectory during the shot attempt.
Milton (PHI) jumps and returns to the floor before releasing the ball.
Harris (PHI) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).
Collins (ATL) legally contests Embiid's (PHI) jump shot attempt.
Korkmaz (PHI) commits a take foul on Gallinari (ATL).
Collins (ATL) legally contests Harris' (PHI) jump shot attempt.
Capela (ATL) reaches in and marginal contact occurs with Embiid (PHI) during his shot attempt.
Milton (PHI) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).
Collins (ATL) legally contests Harris' (PHI) jump shot attempt.
